-->
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=ef90961bb306c24961d850d2a32d8a83 sig_cn_org=d7df98fa54c153f840fb6c0642031237 source=16.8 
     <para>
      Fix race condition that could cause failure to add a newly-inserted
      catalog entry to a catalog cache list (Heikki Linnakangas)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;91fc447c2">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      修复可能导致无法将新插入的目录条目添加到目录缓存列表的竞争条件
      （Heikki Linnakangas）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;91fc447c2">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=ef90961bb306c24961d850d2a32d8a83 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=6378217d148869066d8692a75afabbb4 sig_cn_org=97771a5d2e365db1b0280404bc10b418 source=16.8 
     <para>
      This could result, for example, in failure to use a newly-created
      function within an existing session.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      例如，这可能导致在现有会话中无法使用新创建的函数。
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=6378217d148869066d8692a75afabbb4 -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
