-->
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=2e832a80337b4034a17f33a3947e8484 sig_cn_org=c4701118524fa3a355fd07310c9140b8 source=16.8 
     <para>
      Ignore nulling-relation marker bits when looking up statistics
      (Richard Guo)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;a1a9120c7">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      查找统计信息时忽略空关系标记位
      （Richard Guo）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;a1a9120c7">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=2e832a80337b4034a17f33a3947e8484 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=9fd71010f7e5e851f7ae40b481fe860e sig_cn_org=eb88593da91a6e34dd5bd924b8ee05a9 source=16.8 
     <para>
      This oversight could lead to failure to use relevant statistics
      about expressions, or to <quote>corrupt MVNDistinct
      entry</quote> errors.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      这种疏忽可能会导致未能使用与表达式相关的统计数据，或者出现
      <quote>损坏的MVNDistinct条目</quote>错误。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=9fd71010f7e5e851f7ae40b481fe860e -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--
Author: Tom Lane <tgl@sss.pgh.pa.us>
Branch: master [bf826ea06] 2025-01-16 20:40:07 -0500
Branch: REL_17_STABLE [0671a71e0] 2025-01-16 20:40:07 -0500
Branch: REL_16_STABLE [94c02bd33] 2025-01-16 20:40:07 -0500
Branch: REL_15_STABLE [724ebebb1] 2025-01-16 20:40:07 -0500
