Branch: REL_13_STABLE [45004f527] 2025-01-16 20:40:07 -0500
-->
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=f78ce8c2ee755289d2e8bd85a86076fb sig_cn_org=4ada109f0526129b9832b770df38e874 source=16.8 
     <para>
      Fix missed expression processing for partition pruning steps
      (Tom Lane)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;94c02bd33">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      修复分区修剪步骤中遗漏的表达式处理
      （Tom Lane）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;94c02bd33">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=f78ce8c2ee755289d2e8bd85a86076fb -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=7e40419983329ce887a17279a31cef2c sig_cn_org=95e1537d42a2e5bd56e770592071b756 source=16.8 
     <para>
      This oversight could lead to <quote>unrecognized node type</quote>
      errors, and perhaps other problems, in queries accessing partitioned
      tables.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      此疏忽可能会导致<quote>未识别的节点类型</quote>错误，以及在访问分区表的查询中
      出现其他问题。
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=7e40419983329ce887a17279a31cef2c -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--
Author: Nathan Bossart <nathan@postgresql.org>
Branch: master [84f1b0b03] 2024-12-17 15:24:45 -0600
Branch: REL_17_STABLE [18452b70a] 2024-12-17 15:24:45 -0600
Branch: REL_16_STABLE [2a7402322] 2024-12-17 15:24:45 -0600
Branch: REL_15_STABLE [9f7b7d516] 2024-12-17 15:24:45 -0600
Branch: REL_14_STABLE [84dc1303c] 2024-12-17 15:24:45 -0600
Branch: REL_13_STABLE [853cef097] 2024-12-17 15:24:45 -0600
-->
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=fe49c7cf10b2050d5da39e992d88dde2 sig_cn_org=b75dcf9b601645403d169c692eb0b9c4 source=16.8 
     <para>
      Allow dshash tables to grow past 1GB (Matthias van de Meent)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;2a7402322">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      允许dshash表增长超过1GB（Matthias van de Meent）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;2a7402322">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=fe49c7cf10b2050d5da39e992d88dde2 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=347750289e9d83521dfb408e0fbe72a5 sig_cn_org=e85bfae3f0d7ce3d28ea6b07ea906136 source=16.8 
     <para>
      This avoids errors like <quote>invalid DSA memory alloc request
      size</quote>.  The case can occur for example in transactions that
      process several million tables.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      这可以避免类似<quote>无效的DSA内存分配请求大小</quote>的错误。此情况可能
      发生在处理数百万张表的事务中。
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=347750289e9d83521dfb408e0fbe72a5 -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--
Author: Michael Paquier <michael@paquier.xyz>
