     <para>
      Fix memory leak in <application>pg_restore</application>
      with zstd-compressed data (Tom Lane)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;8cfff087b">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      修复<application>pg_restore</application>中使用zstd压缩数据时的内存泄漏
      (Tom Lane)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;8cfff087b">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=75751d3aa9754b968596394da61d489a -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=be3282674d726f1dde8518e9c33ed986 sig_cn_org=c81386eed7dd1df7507970cdeff66959 source=16.8 
     <para>
      The leak was per-decompression-operation, so would be most
      noticeable with a dump containing many tables or large objects.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      该泄漏是每次解压操作发生的，因此在包含许多表或大对象的转储中会最为明显。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=be3282674d726f1dde8518e9c33ed986 -->
    </listitem>

