<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=d4745fda67fc4072e146f56f98ab1210 sig_cn_org=f1a6f7c03dc9793e91ba428bb54e9a3c source=16.8 
     <para>
      Prevent trusted PL/Perl code from changing environment variables
      (Andrew Dunstan, Noah Misch)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;8fe3e697a">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;88269df4d">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;168579e23">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;c335264c9">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;64df88700">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      防止受信任的PL/Perl代码更改环境变量
      （Andrew Dunstan，Noah Misch）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;8fe3e697a">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;88269df4d">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;168579e23">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;c335264c9">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;64df88700">&sect;</ulink>
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=d4745fda67fc4072e146f56f98ab1210 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=bd709fcc63d81f0beaaf74b9f8cf2384 sig_cn_org=3cca7eba55ed1af1d2f8cc98181e8e7e source=16.8 
     <para>
      The ability to manipulate process environment variables such
      as <literal>PATH</literal> gives an attacker opportunities to
      execute arbitrary code.  Therefore, <quote>trusted</quote> PLs must
      not offer the ability to do that.  To fix <literal>plperl</literal>,
      replace <varname>%ENV</varname> with a tied hash that rejects any
      modification attempt with a warning.
      Untrusted <literal>plperlu</literal> retains the ability to change
      the environment.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      操作进程环境变量（例如<literal>PATH</literal>）的能力为攻击者提供了执行任意代码的
      机会。因此，<quote>受信任的</quote>PLs必须禁止提供这种能力。为修复<literal>plperl</literal>，
      将<varname>%ENV</varname>替换为一个绑定的哈希表，该哈希表会在任何修改尝试时发出警告。
      不受信任的<literal>plperlu</literal>仍然保留更改环境的能力。
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=bd709fcc63d81f0beaaf74b9f8cf2384 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=38ad7fc115832beb61c7123b7374984e sig_cn_org=1cd24c40233f82492a84d43f982d74c0 source=16.8 
     <para>
      The <productname>PostgreSQL</productname> Project thanks
      Coby Abrams for reporting this problem.
      (CVE-2024-10979)
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      <productname>PostgreSQL</productname>项目感谢
      Coby Abrams 报告了此问题。
      （CVE-2024-10979）
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=38ad7fc115832beb61c7123b7374984e -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--
