<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=06352093b358b90c90005347bdccac3e sig_cn_org=c8abf96690dacc202b8dc213fb0ed482 source=16.8 
     <para>
      Fix possible <quote>could not find pathkey item to sort</quote>
      error when the output of a <literal>UNION ALL</literal> member query
      needs to be sorted, and the sort column is an expression (Andrei
      Lepikhov, Tom Lane)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;64635c8af">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      修复可能的<quote>无法找到用于排序的路径键项</quote>
      错误，当<literal>UNION ALL</literal>成员查询的输出
      需要排序，并且排序列是一个表达式时（Andrei
      Lepikhov, Tom Lane）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;64635c8af">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
