<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=eb91bb4fe5705fca3c0beefd1a5c7a65 sig_cn_org=d25e38f2d8042c915cf83a09c66cf250 source=16.8 
     <para>
      Fix performance regressions involving flattening of subqueries
      underneath outer joins that are later reduced to plain joins
      (Tom Lane)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;80d9c07a4">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      修复涉及在外连接下展平子查询的性能回退问题，这些外连接后来被简化为普通连接
      (Tom Lane)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;80d9c07a4">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=eb91bb4fe5705fca3c0beefd1a5c7a65 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=102081c2d11c9e122adb1eb76c060d5a sig_cn_org=b8c0298c9844544bb3f9e7b039eab10f source=16.8 
     <para>
      v16 failed to optimize some queries as well as prior versions had,
      because of overoptimistic simplification of query-pullup logic.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      v16未能像之前的版本那样优化某些查询，因为查询上拉逻辑的过于乐观简化。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=102081c2d11c9e122adb1eb76c060d5a -->
    </listitem>

