<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=eb037da4b4f278e89fe65c2418e9581e sig_cn_org=75df5ce8439a060e6068b16b5f5de5fc source=16.8 
     <para>
      Avoid invalid memory accesses after skipping an invalid toast index
      during <command>VACUUM FULL</command> (Tender Wang)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;afbd3dc7d">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      在跳过无效的toast索引期间，避免在<command>VACUUM FULL</command>之后
      访问无效的内存（Tender Wang）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;afbd3dc7d">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=eb037da4b4f278e89fe65c2418e9581e -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=7c206499037d0c9382ab0d3a1587ccc1 sig_cn_org=cbd1e7c9454049a2e66c68a8b6d524cf source=16.8 
     <para>
      A list tracking yet-to-be-rebuilt indexes was not properly updated
      in this code path, risking assertion failures or crashes later on.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      在此代码路径中，用于跟踪尚未重建索引的列表未被正确更新，
      可能导致后续的断言失败或崩溃。
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=7c206499037d0c9382ab0d3a1587ccc1 -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
