<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=4cfacc34f77519605a31bcb6cd13b859 sig_cn_org=2d08f16c9a0de93498fb3e48c430fe8f source=16.8 
     <para>
      Avoid <quote>wrong tuple length</quote> failure when dropping a
      database with many ACL (permission) entries (Ayush Tiwari)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;545794515">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;f6991cafa">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      避免在删除具有许多ACL（权限）条目的数据库时出现
      <quote>元组长度错误</quote>的失败（Ayush Tiwari）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;545794515">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;f6991cafa">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=4cfacc34f77519605a31bcb6cd13b859 -->
    </listitem>

