<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=38a5813c6fb69a1e27a82c21dfe13fe2 sig_cn_org=ed2689137d71fbf141da1b4f84035d33 source=16.8 
     <para>
      Allow adjusting the <varname>session_authorization</varname>
      and <varname>role</varname> settings in parallel workers (Tom Lane)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;f3ab5d3a2">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      允许在并行工作者中调整<varname>session_authorization</varname>
      和<varname>role</varname>设置（Tom Lane）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;f3ab5d3a2">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=38a5813c6fb69a1e27a82c21dfe13fe2 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=ac8f519d230a9d7c2263a84026072d7b sig_cn_org=cbc05fd7e8626cb33e69b78a85eb30a7 source=16.8 
     <para>
      Our code intends to allow modifiable server settings to be set by
      function <literal>SET</literal> clauses, but not otherwise within a
      parallel worker.  <literal>SET</literal> clauses failed for these
      two settings, though.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      我们的代码旨在允许通过函数<literal>SET</literal>子句设置可修改的服务器设置，
      但在并行工作者中不能以其他方式设置。然而，这两个设置的
      <literal>SET</literal>子句失败了。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=ac8f519d230a9d7c2263a84026072d7b -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--
Author: Tom Lane <tgl@sss.pgh.pa.us>
