<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=d240197dce46012103c9bc08128f9588 sig_cn_org=5296d52c063942fe29e34b6027119d7a source=16.8 
     <para>
      Parse <application>libpq</application>'s <literal>keepalives</literal>
      connection option in the same way as other integer-valued options
      (Yuto Sasaki)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;65f431aff">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      以与其他整数值选项相同的方式解析<application>libpq</application>的
      <literal>keepalives</literal>连接选项（Yuto Sasaki）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;65f431aff">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=d240197dce46012103c9bc08128f9588 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=c315a4491db894a466090b3d3b732688 sig_cn_org=050c17e210551964c061497a661a58ee source=16.8 
     <para>
      The coding used here rejected trailing whitespace in the option
      value, unlike other cases.  This turns out to be problematic
      in <application>ecpg</application>'s usage, for example.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      此处使用的编码拒绝了选项值中的尾随空格，这与其他情况不同。这在
      <application>ecpg</application>的使用中，例如，结果证明是有问题的。
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=c315a4491db894a466090b3d3b732688 -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
