Branch: REL_15_STABLE [b5a5027c9] 2024-08-08 10:22:45 +0300
Branch: REL_14_STABLE [bb5592cac] 2024-08-08 10:22:39 +0300
Branch: REL_13_STABLE [c943e2aae] 2024-08-08 10:22:30 +0300
Branch: REL_12_STABLE [8b86e289f] 2024-08-08 10:22:04 +0300
-->
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=be77570659c07c96b99be2e7ef7fb002 sig_cn_org=6de56da5e5582e5cb7835ea09fe25e74 source=16.8 
     <para>
      Include the source timeline history
      in <application>pg_rewind</application>'s debug output
      (Heikki Linnakangas)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;e8240dbd8">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      在<application>pg_rewind</application>的调试输出中包含源时间线历史
      （Heikki Linnakangas）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;e8240dbd8">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=be77570659c07c96b99be2e7ef7fb002 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=7e1d147ed9886a304def0fda41dbc50e sig_cn_org=9d3784f1f4264c02a2c862941dc7b22c source=16.8 
     <para>
      This was the intention to begin with, but a coding error caused the
      source history to always print as empty.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      这本来是最初的意图，但一个编码错误导致源历史总是显示为空。
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=7e1d147ed9886a304def0fda41dbc50e -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
