<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=73121e52f922c7943e566d60a558c530 sig_cn_org=695277eadea4148a0b7786745ac767c9 source=16.8 
     <para>
      Avoid trying to reindex temporary tables and indexes
      in <application>vacuumdb</application> and in
      parallel <application>reindexdb</application> (VaibhaveS, Michael
      Paquier, Fujii Masao, Nathan Bossart)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;1ea4d9c00">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;653ce5b8b">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;eba8cc1af">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      避免尝试在<application>vacuumdb</application>和并行
      <application>reindexdb</application>中重新索引临时表和索引
      （VaibhaveS，Michael Paquier，Fujii Masao，Nathan Bossart）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;1ea4d9c00">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;653ce5b8b">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;eba8cc1af">&sect;</ulink>
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=73121e52f922c7943e566d60a558c530 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=34c328ba0944bd84514dac2d3c94f08c sig_cn_org=1bf681a0648f3d050896cb34c6d8d81e source=16.8 
     <para>
      Reindexing other sessions' temporary tables cannot work, but the
      check to skip them was missing in some code paths, leading to
      unwanted failures.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      重新索引其他会话的临时表无法正常工作，但某些代码路径中缺少跳过它们的
      检查，导致了不必要的失败。
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=34c328ba0944bd84514dac2d3c94f08c -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
