<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=19c5da912e6972df1b7eb86d0ac4a4cf sig_cn_org=891293f5af12d32b27288adc94168073 source=16.8 
     <para>
      Avoid incorrect results from Merge Right Anti Join plans
      (Richard Guo)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;507f2347e">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      避免合并右反连接计划中的错误结果
      （Richard Guo）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;507f2347e">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=19c5da912e6972df1b7eb86d0ac4a4cf -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=e0aba283dee953f882ea061ca4019fab sig_cn_org=88cf585774d9b5a96458a0f7ce830e74 source=16.8 
     <para>
      If the inner relation is known to have unique join keys, the merge
      could misbehave when there are duplicated join keys in the outer
      relation.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      如果已知内部关系具有唯一的连接键，当外部关系中存在重复的连接键时，
      合并可能会出现异常行为。
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=e0aba283dee953f882ea061ca4019fab -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--
