<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=2d835f50d83c44a5fa503e78f68e7124 sig_cn_org=2d99a2a663696e910f50d2ce5e1ee6ff source=16.8 
     <para>
      Prevent infinite loop in <command>VACUUM</command>
      (Melanie Plageman)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;06bf404cd">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      防止在<command>VACUUM</command>中出现无限循环
      （Melanie Plageman）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;06bf404cd">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=2d835f50d83c44a5fa503e78f68e7124 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=e3be1f1fe413ee4fa9ea5d0ddb7f7468 sig_cn_org=1275d06abc1f9d7d5d9ed8d529a71de9 source=16.8 
     <para>
      After a disconnected standby server with an old running transaction
      reconnected to the primary, it was possible
      for <command>VACUUM</command> on the primary to get confused about
      which tuples are removable, resulting in an infinite loop.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      当一个带有旧运行事务的断开连接的备用服务器重新连接到主服务器时，
      主服务器上的<command>VACUUM</command>可能会对哪些元组是可移除的感到困惑，
      从而导致无限循环。
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=e3be1f1fe413ee4fa9ea5d0ddb7f7468 -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
