      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;6f6b0f193">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      修复<function>pg_size_pretty()</function>函数在应用于最小可能
      <type>bigint</type>值时的结果 (Joseph Koshakow)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;6f6b0f193">&sect;</ulink>
