     <para>
      Avoid non-thread-safe usage of <function>strerror()</function>
      in <application>libpq</application> (Peter Eisentraut)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;c53016860">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      避免在<application>libpq</application>中非线程安全地使用
      <function>strerror()</function>（Peter Eisentraut）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;c53016860">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=62eb56edc15deab85f5f65c5fa586dc6 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=0806c3b74b76ef834eb84c8e0f5fd1bb sig_cn_org=a2214533fa6995290b9486c3681fbc06 source=16.8 
     <para>
      Certain error messages returned by OpenSSL could become garbled in
      multi-threaded applications.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      OpenSSL返回的某些错误消息可能会在多线程应用程序中变得混乱。
</para>
