     <para>
      Fix improper sharing of origin filter condition across
      successive <function>pg_logical_slot_get_changes()</function> calls
      (Hou Zhijie)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;8d05be931">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      修复在连续的<function>pg_logical_slot_get_changes()</function>调用中
      不正确共享原始过滤条件的问题 (侯志杰)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;8d05be931">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=c06be6e32c3b18de6e311459b1f660ce -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=66a9211a6f6f5df257aac9b55ec12974 sig_cn_org=e8601e44179f228be561f620684753af source=16.8 
     <para>
      The origin condition set by one call of this function would be
      re-used by later calls that did not specify the origin argument.
      This was not intended.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      由一次调用此函数设置的起始条件会被后续未指定起始参数的调用重复使用。
      这并非预期的行为。
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=66a9211a6f6f5df257aac9b55ec12974 -->
    </listitem>

