     <para>
      Fix statistics tracking of temporary-table extensions (Karina
      Litskevich, Andres Freund)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;c4758649b">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      修复临时表扩展的统计跟踪（Karina
      Litskevich，Andres Freund）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;c4758649b">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
