<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=17c1add5069346baac2a5b20c41cae6b sig_cn_org=91391a43233a44142563beb0bb12ef57 source=16.8 
     <para>
      Fix <application>pg_dump</application> to dump the
      new <literal>run_as_owner</literal> option of subscriptions
      (Philip Warner)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;67738dbf9">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      修复<application>pg_dump</application>以导出订阅的新
      <literal>run_as_owner</literal>选项（Philip Warner）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;67738dbf9">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=17c1add5069346baac2a5b20c41cae6b -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=da5d08a8aa1a317186ea210162776b43 sig_cn_org=c82012a1c4ba0bb1636f2b2af6a06821 source=16.8 
     <para>
      Due to this oversight, subscriptions would always be restored
      with <literal>run_as_owner</literal> set
      to <literal>false</literal>, which is not equivalent to their
      behavior in pre-v16 releases.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      由于这一疏忽，订阅总是会以<literal>run_as_owner</literal>设置为
      <literal>false</literal>的方式恢复，这与它们在v16之前版本中的行为
      并不相同。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=da5d08a8aa1a317186ea210162776b43 -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--
Author: Tom Lane <tgl@sss.pgh.pa.us>
