     <para>
      Fix failure of <filename>contrib/btree_gin</filename> indexes
      on <type>interval</type> columns,
      when an indexscan using the <literal>&lt;</literal>
      or <literal>&lt;=</literal> operator is performed (Dean Rasheed)
