<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=9eb2422f5b34b1d8bd0b994de63af4d1 sig_cn_org=dad1c67f0b79de801eff3d09d420a2a1 source=16.8 
     <para>
      Suppress assorted build-time warnings on
      recent <productname>macOS</productname> (Tom Lane)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;75c562653">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;e73d6a0df">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      抑制在最近的<productname>macOS</productname>上出现的各种构建时警告
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;75c562653">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;e73d6a0df">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=9eb2422f5b34b1d8bd0b994de63af4d1 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=11974fcd2483573f3a0f7d8cf52b8e43 sig_cn_org=85d6138033477a834597ce3946ca0a84 source=15.7 
     <para>
      <productname>Xcode 15</productname> (released
      with <productname>macOS Sonoma</productname>) changed the linker's
      behavior in a way that causes many duplicate-library warnings while
      building <productname>PostgreSQL</productname>.  These were
      harmless, but they're annoying so avoid citing the same libraries
      twice.  Also remove use of the <option>-multiply_defined
      suppress</option> linker switch, which apparently has been a no-op
      for a long time, and is now actively complained of.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      <productname>Xcode 15</productname>（随 <productname>macOS Sonoma</productname> 发布）改变了链接器的行为，导致构建 <productname>PostgreSQL</productname> 时出现许多重复库警告。这些警告是无害的，但很烦人，因此避免引用相同的库两次。还要删除使用 <option>-multiply_defined suppress</option> 链接器开关，这个开关显然很长时间以来都是无效的，现在却被积极投诉。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=11974fcd2483573f3a0f7d8cf52b8e43 -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--
Author: Michael Paquier <michael@paquier.xyz>
Branch: master [6fc3a138b] 2023-09-27 14:40:23 +0900
Branch: REL_16_STABLE [641db601b] 2023-09-27 14:41:15 +0900
Branch: REL_15_STABLE [8a9e4e84e] 2023-09-27 14:41:21 +0900
Branch: REL_14_STABLE [e4d7ad30f] 2023-09-27 14:41:23 +0900
Branch: REL_13_STABLE [a64b8b035] 2023-09-27 14:41:26 +0900
-->
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=08d162372a84e7e1874ea3f1805ac856 sig_cn_org=d9b0cfb28deed3158c86e634ece3c43a source=16.8 
     <para>
      When building <filename>contrib/unaccent</filename>'s rules file,
      fall back to using <literal>python</literal>
      if <literal>-&minus;with-python</literal> was not given and make
      variable <literal>PYTHON</literal> was not set (Japin Li)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;641db601b">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      在构建<filename>contrib/unaccent</filename>的规则文件时，
      如果没有指定<literal>--with-python</literal>并且没有设置
      变量<literal>PYTHON</literal>，则回退使用<literal>python</literal>
      (Japin Li)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;641db601b">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=08d162372a84e7e1874ea3f1805ac856 -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--
Author: Tom Lane <tgl@sss.pgh.pa.us>
Branch: master [5fd3e06f6] 2023-10-28 11:54:40 -0400
Branch: REL_16_STABLE [d1537afe3] 2023-10-28 11:54:51 -0400
Branch: REL_15_STABLE [85b98a70b] 2023-10-28 11:54:59 -0400
Branch: REL_14_STABLE [877e7b4b9] 2023-10-28 11:55:06 -0400
Branch: REL_13_STABLE [d94612873] 2023-10-28 11:55:14 -0400
Branch: REL_12_STABLE [7180bb827] 2023-10-28 11:55:22 -0400
Branch: REL_11_STABLE [64fc5e005] 2023-10-28 11:55:30 -0400
-->
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=b00e02aca95763e41c78b1af449ae8b7 sig_cn_org=4c0a458787cce5eef053465812fa1dca source=16.8 
     <para>
      Remove <literal>PHOT</literal> (Phoenix Islands Time) from the
      default timezone abbreviations list (Tom Lane)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;d1537afe3">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      从默认时区缩写列表中移除<literal>PHOT</literal>（凤凰群岛时间）
      （Tom Lane）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;d1537afe3">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=b00e02aca95763e41c78b1af449ae8b7 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=846a055d12175353d57c3ac3b27f66d0 sig_cn_org=e0c37e87724f69aa508d1a722b84ba3c source=15.7 
     <para>
      Presence of this abbreviation in the default list can cause failures
      on recent Debian and Ubuntu releases, as they no longer install the
      underlying tzdb entry by default.  Since this is a made-up
      abbreviation for a zone with a total human population of about two
      dozen, it seems unlikely that anyone will miss it.  If someone does,
      they can put it back via a custom abbreviations file.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      默认列表中存在这个缩写词可能会导致在最近的Debian和Ubuntu发行版上失败，
      因为它们不再默认安装底层的tzdb条目。由于这是一个为大约两打人口的区域
      捏造的缩写词，似乎不太可能有人会错过它。如果有人错过了，他们可以通
      过自定义缩写文件将其恢复。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=846a055d12175353d57c3ac3b27f66d0 -->
    </listitem>

   </itemizedlist>

  </sect2>
 </sect1>

 <sect1 id="release-16">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=27a26fcaf93e375bc35db1b2c6022bcb sig_cn_org=a9365c6f26f16e4b922a53fab1bdeef1 source=16.8 
  <title>Release 16</title>
________________________________________________________-->
  <title>发布版本16</title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=27a26fcaf93e375bc35db1b2c6022bcb -->

  <formalpara>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=c45e8127eac45f2347bf1713afaeffda sig_cn_org=253305b4c6dff5b87ef36e3c2d95e52e source=15.7 
   <title>Release date:</title>
________________________________________________________-->
   <title>发布日期：</title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=c45e8127eac45f2347bf1713afaeffda -->
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=b5f5398535f61bdae37e9de9d5f6f27b sig_cn_org=b5f5398535f61bdae37e9de9d5f6f27b source=16.8 
   <para>2023-09-14</para>
________________________________________________________-->
   <para>2023-09-14</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=b5f5398535f61bdae37e9de9d5f6f27b -->
  </formalpara>

  <sect2 id="release-16-highlights">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=13508788fd8dee2d1f9c928870e99338 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
   <title>Overview</title>
________________________________________________________-->
   <title>概述</title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=13508788fd8dee2d1f9c928870e99338 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=2c95673e9e5dc4052aa7c30f2815aef8 sig_cn_org=825c70b06d9d8c6d3e65d985a7def04c source=16.8 
   <para>
    <productname>PostgreSQL</productname> 16 contains many new features
    and enhancements, including:
   </para>
________________________________________________________-->
   <para>
    <productname>PostgreSQL</productname> 16 包含许多新功能和改进，包括：
   </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=2c95673e9e5dc4052aa7c30f2815aef8 -->

   <itemizedlist>

    <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=b280a4c116f0a220954d2c218ce6c58b sig_cn_org=f077365c4ea43bf3385c8a30ed359c0d source=16.8 
     <para>
      Allow parallelization of <literal>FULL</literal> and internal right <literal>OUTER</literal> hash joins
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      允许并行化<literal>FULL</literal>和内部右<literal>OUTER</literal>哈希连接
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=b280a4c116f0a220954d2c218ce6c58b -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=aed0fd31b7e98c1f4015119c72141b5f sig_cn_org=6c5f2354df7395182d22d8be4a13bd96 source=16.8 
     <para>
      Allow logical replication from standby servers
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      允许从备用服务器进行逻辑复制
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=aed0fd31b7e98c1f4015119c72141b5f -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=9c52707b5092c4e183bab6282f0ac9ff sig_cn_org=fd945e3a82b3ce68f2306f44667e22ac source=16.8 
     <para>
      Allow logical replication subscribers to apply large transactions in parallel
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      允许逻辑复制订阅者并行应用大型事务
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=9c52707b5092c4e183bab6282f0ac9ff -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=ff1b21d34e6462d3940f2c6f8a86a42e sig_cn_org=8cc8ec71b01c4669cdc86196df510110 source=16.8 
     <para>
      Allow monitoring of <acronym>I/O</acronym> statistics using the new <structname>pg_stat_io</structname> view
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      允许通过新的<structname>pg_stat_io</structname>视图监控<acronym>I/O</acronym>统计信息
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=ff1b21d34e6462d3940f2c6f8a86a42e -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=16fcf72b8d19a591f714e4d0c64aedd2 sig_cn_org=1324f0871585d0e479f4c13e33fc51ef source=16.8 
     <para>
      Add <acronym>SQL/JSON</acronym> constructors and identity functions
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      添加<acronym>SQL/JSON</acronym>构造函数和标识函数
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=16fcf72b8d19a591f714e4d0c64aedd2 -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=3f867bc9c179c3de12b119b73b62df9b sig_cn_org=80f21a5e00ad30d1e48b3f15eec65d34 source=16.8 
     <para>
      Improve performance of vacuum freezing
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      提高真空冻结的性能
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=3f867bc9c179c3de12b119b73b62df9b -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=31a205eb2bc1071703153727d8322b1e sig_cn_org=34eadb649a0cb98e9e0f4de93ff349cc source=16.8 
     <para>
      Add support for regular expression matching of user and database names in <filename>pg_hba.conf</filename>, and user names in <filename>pg_ident.conf</filename>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      在<filename>pg_hba.conf</filename>中添加对用户和数据库名称的正则表达式匹配支持，
      以及在<filename>pg_ident.conf</filename>中对用户名的正则表达式匹配支持。
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=31a205eb2bc1071703153727d8322b1e -->
    </listitem>

   </itemizedlist>

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=304a471d1052301a1fe963dfab1b6622 sig_cn_org=e5f7f998bc712f46c6556efbb8f477db source=16.8 
   <para>
    The above items and other new features of
    <productname>PostgreSQL</productname> 16 are explained in more detail
    in the sections below.
   </para>
________________________________________________________-->
   <para>
    上述项目和其他<productname>PostgreSQL</productname> 16的新功能将在下面的章节中
    进行更详细的解释。
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=304a471d1052301a1fe963dfab1b6622 -->

  </sect2>

  <sect2  id="release-16-migration">

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=b8a6cb687d0585ee2fb208fd2abdbd96 sig_cn_org=d22ef1287f4cafc599090acf911cb132 source=16.8 
   <title>Migration to Version 16</title>
________________________________________________________-->
   <title>迁移到版本16</title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=b8a6cb687d0585ee2fb208fd2abdbd96 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=5b9f61db6c635ea82b92aa17abd61182 sig_cn_org=186150cca28661dd1b0ab789cfdf3f47 source=16.8 
   <para>
    A dump/restore using <xref linkend="app-pg-dumpall"/> or use of
    <xref linkend="pgupgrade"/> or logical replication is required for
    those wishing to migrate data from any previous release.  See <xref
    linkend="upgrading"/> for general information on migrating to new
    major releases.
   </para>
________________________________________________________-->
   <para>
    需要使用<xref linkend="app-pg-dumpall"/>进行转储/恢复，或者使用
    <xref linkend="pgupgrade"/>或逻辑复制来迁移数据，以从任何先前版本迁移。
    有关迁移到新主要版本的一般信息，请参阅<xref linkend="upgrading"/>。
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=5b9f61db6c635ea82b92aa17abd61182 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=712a164462bc6b1faf2693af89368e7e sig_cn_org=1e695aea130b4ea9e7bccf9b9fd8d744 source=16.8 
   <para>
    Version 16 contains a number of changes that may affect compatibility
    with previous releases.  Observe the following incompatibilities:
   </para>
________________________________________________________-->
   <para>
    版本16包含许多可能影响与以前版本兼容性的更改。请注意以下不兼容之处：
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=712a164462bc6b1faf2693af89368e7e -->

   <itemizedlist>

<!--
Author: Tom Lane <tgl@sss.pgh.pa.us>
2023-01-01 [d747dc85a] In plpgsql, don't preassign portal names to bound cursor
-->

    <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=1407806e2cee1b93b469c6bafcb417c7 sig_cn_org=65fbdd25ccd7584de854ffd7c6c18a92 source=16.8 
     <para>
      Change assignment rules for <link
      linkend="plpgsql-open-bound-cursor"><application>PL/pgSQL</application></link>
      bound cursor variables (Tom Lane)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;d747dc85a">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      更改分配规则以适用于<link
      linkend="plpgsql-open-bound-cursor"><application>PL/pgSQL</application></link>
      绑定的游标变量（Tom Lane）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;d747dc85a">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=1407806e2cee1b93b469c6bafcb417c7 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=33ee74ae7d467d0baabe08cf3ac02338 sig_cn_org=994bad56d42ffd67fa8b464e4ad1a7e5 source=16.8 
     <para>
      Previously, the string value of such variables
      was set to match the variable name during cursor
      assignment;  now it will be assigned during <link
      linkend="plpgsql-cursor-opening"><command>OPEN</command></link>,
      and will not match the variable name.  To restore the previous
      behavior, assign the desired portal name to the cursor variable
      before <command>OPEN</command>.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      以前，这类变量的字符串值在游标赋值期间会设置为与变量名匹配；
      现在将在<link linkend="plpgsql-cursor-opening"><command>OPEN</command></link>
      期间分配，并且不会与变量名匹配。要恢复以前的行为，请在
      <command>OPEN</command>之前将所需的门户名称分配给游标变量。
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=33ee74ae7d467d0baabe08cf3ac02338 -->
    </listitem>

<!--
Author: Daniel Gustafsson <dgustafsson@postgresql.org>
2023-02-24 [d95952325] Disallow NULLS NOT DISTINCT indexes for primary keys
-->

    <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=5d27880b529d39c334abec625f2f1851 sig_cn_org=4a5c2746b5869f5ca15a72052bb76c4b source=16.8 
     <para>
      Disallow <link linkend="sql-createindex"><literal>NULLS NOT
      DISTINCT</literal></link> indexes for primary keys (Daniel
      Gustafsson)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;d95952325">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      禁止<link linkend="sql-createindex"><literal>NULLS NOT
      DISTINCT</literal></link>索引用于主键（Daniel
      Gustafsson）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;d95952325">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=5d27880b529d39c334abec625f2f1851 -->
    </listitem>

<!--
Author: Michael Paquier <michael@paquier.xyz>
2022-07-19 [2cbc3c17a] Rework logic and simplify syntax of REINDEX DATABASE/SYS
Author: Michael Paquier <michael@paquier.xyz>
2022-07-26 [0a5f06b84] Fix a few issues with REINDEX grammar
-->

    <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=56d3d692628f9f42fd050ef8e940ea3c sig_cn_org=b73df342f2b75471f977a7a5d3d86ab0 source=16.8 
     <para>
      Change <link linkend="sql-reindex"><command>REINDEX
      DATABASE</command></link> and <link
      linkend="app-reindexdb"><application>reindexdb</application></link>
      to not process indexes on system catalogs (Simon Riggs)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;2cbc3c17a">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;0a5f06b84">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      更改<link linkend="sql-reindex"><command>REINDEX
      DATABASE</command></link>和<link
      linkend="app-reindexdb"><application>reindexdb</application></link>
      以不处理系统目录上的索引（Simon Riggs）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;2cbc3c17a">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;0a5f06b84">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=56d3d692628f9f42fd050ef8e940ea3c -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=b2b5fd3dace993b8860cf3c2b126b56d sig_cn_org=b8a1692d324be64f26399dd60bc29829 source=16.8 
     <para>
      Processing such indexes is still possible using <command>REINDEX
      SYSTEM</command> and <link linkend="app-reindexdb"><command>reindexdb
      -&minus;system</command></link>.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      处理这样的索引仍然可以通过使用<command>REINDEX SYSTEM</command>和
      <link linkend="app-reindexdb"><command>reindexdb --system</command></link>来完成。
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=b2b5fd3dace993b8860cf3c2b126b56d -->
    </listitem>

<!--
Author: Tom Lane <tgl@sss.pgh.pa.us>
2023-01-11 [8bf6ec3ba] Improve handling of inherited GENERATED expressions.
-->

    <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=5c4873338892f9b5b5e6bf825e8ae9e6 sig_cn_org=a173efa8db9f6920c9b9e8e7eecd974d source=16.8 
     <para>
      Tighten <link
      linkend="ddl-generated-columns"><literal>GENERATED</literal></link>
      expression restrictions on inherited and partitioned tables (Amit
      Langote, Tom Lane)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;8bf6ec3ba">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      收紧继承和分区表上的<link
      linkend="ddl-generated-columns"><literal>GENERATED</literal></link>
      表达式限制（Amit Langote，Tom Lane）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;8bf6ec3ba">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=5c4873338892f9b5b5e6bf825e8ae9e6 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=da6c14e1302e9c044462ef19b5b97301 sig_cn_org=8b519d102736388598564e960d4e7091 source=16.8 
     <para>
      Columns of parent/partitioned and child/partition tables must all
      have the same generation status, though now the actual generation
      expressions can be different.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      父/分区表和子/分区表的列必须具有相同的生成状态，尽管现在实际的生成
      表达式可以不同。
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=da6c14e1302e9c044462ef19b5b97301 -->
    </listitem>

<!--
Author: Michael Paquier <michael@paquier.xyz>
2023-03-14 [5c1b66280] Rework design of functions in pg_walinspect
-->

    <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=a19345bcc892c2ef8f26695d3fc437a0 sig_cn_org=56c6b04572d083b7817d1d4955554309 source=16.8 
     <para>
      Remove <link
      linkend="pgwalinspect"><application>pg_walinspect</application></link>
      functions
      <function>pg_get_wal_records_info_till_end_of_wal()</function>
      and <function>pg_get_wal_stats_till_end_of_wal()</function>
      (Bharath Rupireddy)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;5c1b66280">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      移除<link
      linkend="pgwalinspect"><application>pg_walinspect</application></link>
      函数
      <function>pg_get_wal_records_info_till_end_of_wal()</function>
      和<function>pg_get_wal_stats_till_end_of_wal()</function>
      （Bharath Rupireddy）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;5c1b66280">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=a19345bcc892c2ef8f26695d3fc437a0 -->
    </listitem>

<!--
Author: David Rowley <drowley@postgresql.org>
2023-02-15 [5352ca22e] Rename force_parallel_mode to debug_parallel_query
Author: David Rowley <drowley@postgresql.org>
2023-04-14 [0981846b9] Remove old GUC name mapping for "force_parallel_mode"
-->

