<!--
Author: Daniel Gustafsson <dgustafsson@postgresql.org>
2023-04-07 [7d71d3dd0] Refresh cost-based delay params more frequently in autov
Author: Daniel Gustafsson <dgustafsson@postgresql.org>
2023-04-20 [a9781ae11] Fix autovacuum cost debug logging
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=906e00f30abdb5ec283a503d024a24a7 sig_cn_org=c38a719fe539bc44fe70aa9942a0e6fc source=16.8 
       <para>
        Allow <link linkend="autovacuum">autovacuum</link> to more
        frequently honor changes to delay settings (Melanie Plageman)
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;7d71d3dd0">&sect;</ulink>
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;a9781ae11">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        允许 <link linkend="autovacuum">自动清理</link> 更频繁地遵守延迟设置的更改
        （Melanie Plageman）
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;7d71d3dd0">&sect;</ulink>
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;a9781ae11">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=906e00f30abdb5ec283a503d024a24a7 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=67464cabea08a40851b77c1a64df9480 sig_cn_org=f1f5ea83b1eb2a480e9f59190b50feec source=16.8 
       <para>
        Rather than honor changes only at the start of each relation,
        honor them at the start of each block.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        与其仅在每个关系的开始处处理更改，
        不如在每个块的开始处处理更改。
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=67464cabea08a40851b77c1a64df9480 -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Fujii Masao <fujii@postgresql.org>
2022-07-26 [756e221db] Reduce overhead of renaming archive status files.
Author: Fujii Masao <fujii@postgresql.org>
2022-07-26 [3cabe45a8] doc: Add note about re-archiving of same WAL files in do
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=1d1f27c8d1af100f2191d0ca4b0dd49b sig_cn_org=01e120b5864ba2d0ded8e93249d5ec30 source=16.8 
       <para>
        Remove restrictions that archive files be durably renamed
        (Nathan Bossart)
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;756e221db">&sect;</ulink>
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;3cabe45a8">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        移除对存档文件必须被持久重命名的限制
        （Nathan Bossart）
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;756e221db">&sect;</ulink>
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;3cabe45a8">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=1d1f27c8d1af100f2191d0ca4b0dd49b -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=9b50b93a2d81c128800aaf5c19954d67 sig_cn_org=3fc6c3d1f8c2fdf97186f04cccf1e6af source=16.8 
       <para>
        The <link
        linkend="guc-archive-command"><varname>archive_command</varname></link>
        command is now more likely to be called with already-archived
        files after a crash.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        <link
        linkend="guc-archive-command"><varname>archive_command</varname></link>
        命令现在更有可能在崩溃后被调用时处理已经归档的文件。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=9b50b93a2d81c128800aaf5c19954d67 -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Peter Eisentraut <peter@eisentraut.org>
2022-11-15 [d627ce3b7] Disallow setting archive_library and archive_command at
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=db23edb198371cab53132e5c940d9838 sig_cn_org=77b27a4dad6c531e110fff4e0ac771f7 source=16.8 
       <para>
        Prevent <link
        linkend="guc-archive-library"><varname>archive_library</varname></link>
        and <link
        linkend="guc-archive-command"><varname>archive_command</varname></link>
        from being set at the same time (Nathan Bossart)
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;d627ce3b7">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        防止<link
        linkend="guc-archive-library"><varname>archive_library</varname></link>
        和<link
        linkend="guc-archive-command"><varname>archive_command</varname></link>
