        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;d627ce3b7">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=db23edb198371cab53132e5c940d9838 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=6ba35e8c8e16775d867653de2d13bef9 sig_cn_org=d6c68f297354b2e68b09085d382ff6ca source=16.8 
       <para>
        Previously <varname>archive_library</varname> would override
        <varname>archive_command</varname>.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        之前<varname>archive_library</varname>会覆盖
        <varname>archive_command</varname>。
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=6ba35e8c8e16775d867653de2d13bef9 -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Tom Lane <tgl@sss.pgh.pa.us>
2022-11-21 [51b5834cd] Provide options for postmaster to kill child processes w
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=5b02c6b89d21db65c66ea4f788933b2b sig_cn_org=f3e043f8a094f0f427a5f5f0f9386e66 source=16.8 
       <para>
        Allow the postmaster to terminate children with an abort signal
        (Tom Lane)
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;51b5834cd">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        允许邮局管理员通过中止信号终止子进程
        （Tom Lane）
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;51b5834cd">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=5b02c6b89d21db65c66ea4f788933b2b -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=7f6d93b05198d22129186911c4dd83b2 sig_cn_org=0ebb7d38806774999dec5f8bdf32bbd2 source=16.8 
       <para>
        This allows collection of a core dump for a
        stuck child process.  This is controlled by <link
        linkend="guc-send-abort-for-crash"><varname>send_abort_for_crash</varname></link>
        and <link
        linkend="guc-send-abort-for-kill"><varname>send_abort_for_kill</varname></link>.
        The postmaster's <option>-T</option> switch is now the same as
        setting <varname>send_abort_for_crash</varname>.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        这允许为卡住的子进程收集核心转储。这由<link
        linkend="guc-send-abort-for-crash"><varname>send_abort_for_crash</varname></link>
        和<link
        linkend="guc-send-abort-for-kill"><varname>send_abort_for_kill</varname></link>
        控制。主进程的<option>-T</option>开关现在等同于设置
        <varname>send_abort_for_crash</varname>。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=7f6d93b05198d22129186911c4dd83b2 -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Tom Lane <tgl@sss.pgh.pa.us>
2022-11-21 [51b5834cd] Provide options for postmaster to kill child processes w
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=72c07e64a773d1da10c497b680d15adb sig_cn_org=6d61cac487dd92b625a592571cfefa74 source=16.8 
       <para>
        Remove the non-functional postmaster <option>-n</option> option
        (Tom Lane)
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;51b5834cd">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        移除非功能性的postmaster <option>-n</option> 选项
        （Tom Lane）
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;51b5834cd">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=72c07e64a773d1da10c497b680d15adb -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Robert Haas <rhaas@postgresql.org>
2023-01-20 [6e2775e4d] Add new GUC reserved_connections.
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=b85f0770fb876ecf0716405d4bd5273f sig_cn_org=127ea7236bd1bc7c4033f15074685d23 source=16.8 
       <para>
        Allow the server to reserve backend slots for roles with <link
        linkend="predefined-roles"><literal>pg_use_reserved_connections</literal></link>
        membership (Nathan Bossart)
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;6e2775e4d">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        允许服务器为具有<link
        linkend="predefined-roles"><literal>pg_use_reserved_connections</literal></link>
        成员资格的角色保留后端插槽（Nathan Bossart）
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;6e2775e4d">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=b85f0770fb876ecf0716405d4bd5273f -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=8a34467547782ef3931ba9c1df302b32 sig_cn_org=33411c2b1e96cff3f8415fc573a68e18 source=16.8 
       <para>
        The number of reserved slots is set by server variable <link
        linkend="guc-reserved-connections"><varname>reserved_connections</varname></link>.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        保留的槽位数量由服务器变量<link
        linkend="guc-reserved-connections"><varname>reserved_connections</varname></link>设置。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=8a34467547782ef3931ba9c1df302b32 -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Michael Paquier <michael@paquier.xyz>
2022-09-17 [fdd8937c0] Fix huge_pages on Windows
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=4a83bb004efa5f03e2a18136670e1367 sig_cn_org=15864e549d9cfbec663b5c97c9f718d3 source=16.8 
       <para>
        Allow <link linkend="guc-huge-pages">huge pages</link> to
        work on newer versions of <systemitem class="osname">Windows
        10</systemitem> (Thomas Munro)
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;fdd8937c0">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        允许<link linkend="guc-huge-pages">大页</link>在较新版本的
        <systemitem class="osname">Windows 10</systemitem>上工作
        （Thomas Munro）
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;fdd8937c0">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=4a83bb004efa5f03e2a18136670e1367 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=7500e5dafe0f034ff6c394ddb130f232 sig_cn_org=05038b08c466d0de9db9ff1172a0f5df source=16.8 
       <para>
        This adds the special handling required to enable huge pages
        on newer versions of <systemitem class="osname">Windows
        10</systemitem>.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        这增加了在较新版本的<systemitem class="osname">Windows
        10</systemitem>上启用大页面所需的特殊处理。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=7500e5dafe0f034ff6c394ddb130f232 -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Thomas Munro <tmunro@postgresql.org>
2023-04-08 [d4e71df6d] Add io_direct setting (developer-only).
Author: Thomas Munro <tmunro@postgresql.org>
2023-05-15 [319bae9a8] Rename io_direct to debug_io_direct.
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=13aae53ae42eefe87c7bfee584d0c92e sig_cn_org=a0d1a194463c2e0d8122d35e4e8de12a source=16.8 
       <para>
        Add <link
        linkend="guc-debug-io-direct"><varname>debug_io_direct</varname></link>
        setting for developer usage (Thomas Munro, Andres Freund,
        Bharath Rupireddy)
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;d4e71df6d">&sect;</ulink>
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;319bae9a8">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        添加 <link
        linkend="guc-debug-io-direct"><varname>debug_io_direct</varname></link>
        设置以供开发者使用（Thomas Munro, Andres Freund,
        Bharath Rupireddy）
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;d4e71df6d">&sect;</ulink>
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;319bae9a8">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=13aae53ae42eefe87c7bfee584d0c92e -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=67ebc0279ba73de78cd43323e0e6bda6 sig_cn_org=67b7afb8bc301a889933f1a2527b1cf9 source=16.8 
       <para>
        While primarily for developers, <link
        linkend="guc-wal-sync-method"><literal>wal_sync_method=open_sync</literal></link>/<literal>open_datasync</literal>
        has been modified to not use direct <acronym>I/O</acronym> with
        <literal>wal_level=minimal</literal>;  this is now enabled with
        <literal>debug_io_direct=wal</literal>.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        虽然主要是为开发者设计的，<link
        linkend="guc-wal-sync-method"><literal>wal_sync_method=open_sync</literal></link>/
        <literal>open_datasync</literal>已被修改为不使用直接<acronym>I/O</acronym>
        与<literal>wal_level=minimal</literal>；现在可以通过
        <literal>debug_io_direct=wal</literal>启用。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=67ebc0279ba73de78cd43323e0e6bda6 -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Michael Paquier <michael@paquier.xyz>
2022-12-20 [cca186348] Add pg_dissect_walfile_name()
Author: Michael Paquier <michael@paquier.xyz>
2022-12-23 [13e0d7a60] Rename pg_dissect_walfile_name() to pg_split_walfile_nam
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=03480cfd7374120f25fcf20091bd3c0d sig_cn_org=2db4384d009aea7a7fb32c0d2f82a512 source=16.8 
       <para>
        Add function <link
        linkend="functions-admin-backup-table"><function>pg_split_walfile_name()</function></link>
        to report the segment and timeline values of <acronym>WAL</acronym>
        file names (Bharath Rupireddy)
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;cca186348">&sect;</ulink>
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;13e0d7a60">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        添加函数<link
        linkend="functions-admin-backup-table"><function>pg_split_walfile_name()</function></link>
        用于报告<acronym>WAL</acronym>文件名的段和时间线值
        （Bharath Rupireddy）
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;cca186348">&sect;</ulink>
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;13e0d7a60">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=03480cfd7374120f25fcf20091bd3c0d -->
      </listitem>

     </itemizedlist>

    </sect4>

    <sect4 id="release-16-pg-hba">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=06472fb7302ac18946eb5fe4c4ee8a35 sig_cn_org=a24d673cf64ef9072374d5c1a57983d1 source=16.8 
     <title><link linkend="auth-pg-hba-conf">pg_hba.conf</link></title>
________________________________________________________-->
     <title><link linkend="auth-pg-hba-conf">pg_hba.conf</link></title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=06472fb7302ac18946eb5fe4c4ee8a35 -->

     <itemizedlist>

<!--
Author: Michael Paquier <michael@paquier.xyz>
2022-10-24 [8fea86830] Add support for regexps on database and user entries in
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=637f1b2f07ae2d7856e649de3df12011 sig_cn_org=37fdb84a2f24b40274ebae8c3eb2f112 source=16.8 
       <para>
        Add support for regular expression matching on database and role
        entries in <filename>pg_hba.conf</filename> (Bertrand Drouvot)
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;8fea86830">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        增加对在<filename>pg_hba.conf</filename>中对数据库和角色条目进行正则表达式匹配
        的支持 (Bertrand Drouvot)
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;8fea86830">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=637f1b2f07ae2d7856e649de3df12011 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=66a9f9695a8b18f961735daf712af64e sig_cn_org=1a7e5d99ea8f11bd46f53fa0a2206a09 source=16.8 
       <para>
        Regular expression patterns are prefixed with a slash.  Database
        and role names that begin with slashes need to be double-quoted
        if referenced in <filename>pg_hba.conf</filename>.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        正则表达式模式以斜杠作为前缀。以斜杠开头的数据库和角色名称在
        <filename>pg_hba.conf</filename>中引用时需要用双引号括起来。
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=66a9f9695a8b18f961735daf712af64e -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Michael Paquier <michael@paquier.xyz>
2023-01-20 [efb6f4a4f] Support the same patterns for pg-user in pg_ident.conf a
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=52c0ffd38fbdc938c4119011da2ad51f sig_cn_org=c966e78f445a72283ad4e4e2b27a72d9 source=16.8 
       <para>
        Improve user-column handling of <link
        linkend="runtime-config-file-locations"><filename>pg_ident.conf</filename></link>
        to match <filename>pg_hba.conf</filename> (Jelte Fennema)
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;efb6f4a4f">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        改进用户列的处理，使其与<link
        linkend="runtime-config-file-locations"><filename>pg_ident.conf</filename></link>
        匹配<filename>pg_hba.conf</filename>（Jelte Fennema）
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;efb6f4a4f">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=52c0ffd38fbdc938c4119011da2ad51f -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=cb444963d7436d29e8bd2b007a52e669 sig_cn_org=9c1d85807c7cc3279643b54d44f67164 source=16.8 
       <para>
        Specifically, add support for <literal>all</literal>, role
        membership with <literal>+</literal>, and regular expressions
        with a leading slash.  Any user name that matches these patterns
        must be double-quoted.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        具体来说，添加对<literal>all</literal>的支持，角色成员资格使用
        <literal>+</literal>，以及以斜杠开头的正则表达式。任何匹配这些模式的
        用户名都必须用双引号括起来。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=cb444963d7436d29e8bd2b007a52e669 -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Michael Paquier <michael@paquier.xyz>
2022-11-24 [a54b658ce] Add support for file inclusions in HBA and ident configu
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=56903cf4baa77a9e910d28f332f3ea90 sig_cn_org=78793ec778f210080807afdedbb423dd source=16.8 
       <para>
        Allow include files in <filename>pg_hba.conf</filename> and
        <filename>pg_ident.conf</filename> (Julien Rouhaud)
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;a54b658ce">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        允许在<filename>pg_hba.conf</filename>和<filename>pg_ident.conf</filename>
        中包含文件（Julien Rouhaud）
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;a54b658ce">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=56903cf4baa77a9e910d28f332f3ea90 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=bef071bc31d8d4f25b5c18f2275ab4d2 sig_cn_org=fc117ba9af0c94173083d182c744a841 source=16.8 
       <para>
        These are controlled by <literal>include</literal>,
        <literal>include_if_exists</literal>, and
        <literal>include_dir</literal>.  System views <link
        linkend="view-pg-hba-file-rules"><structname>pg_hba_file_rules</structname></link>
        and <link
        linkend="view-pg-ident-file-mappings"><structname>pg_ident_file_mappings</structname></link>
        now display the file name.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        这些由<literal>include</literal>、<literal>include_if_exists</literal>和
        <literal>include_dir</literal>控制。系统视图<link
        linkend="view-pg-hba-file-rules"><structname>pg_hba_file_rules</structname></link>
        和<link
        linkend="view-pg-ident-file-mappings"><structname>pg_ident_file_mappings</structname></link>
        现在显示文件名。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=bef071bc31d8d4f25b5c18f2275ab4d2 -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Tom Lane <tgl@sss.pgh.pa.us>
2023-07-27 [de3f0e3fe] Eliminate fixed token-length limit in hba.c.
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=7e493d039a92689ed4166e6639e1931c sig_cn_org=9a8605f3ba8b767ed89675b32d3fb853 source=16.8 
       <para>
        Allow <filename>pg_hba.conf</filename> tokens to be of unlimited
        length (Tom Lane)
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;de3f0e3fe">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        允许<filename>pg_hba.conf</filename>令牌具有无限长度（Tom Lane）
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;de3f0e3fe">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=7e493d039a92689ed4166e6639e1931c -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Michael Paquier <michael@paquier.xyz>
2022-10-26 [c591300a8] Add rule_number to pg_hba_file_rules and map_number to p
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=c6ab4a302d8875c1a7b9df1bec31c588 sig_cn_org=1b9f0e309029cce81db8d2338b23d543 source=16.8 
       <para>
        Add rule and map numbers to the system view <link
        linkend="view-pg-hba-file-rules"><structname>pg_hba_file_rules</structname></link>
        (Julien Rouhaud)
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;c591300a8">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        添加规则并将数字映射到系统视图<link
        linkend="view-pg-hba-file-rules"><structname>pg_hba_file_rules</structname></link>
        （Julien Rouhaud）
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;c591300a8">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=c6ab4a302d8875c1a7b9df1bec31c588 -->
      </listitem>

     </itemizedlist>

    </sect4>

    <sect4 id="release-16-localization">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=2e9a9782eabaaa726ff7af14e8ac1973 sig_cn_org=7dc8bddcb6d5f09654f79e352b323fde source=16.8 
     <title><link linkend="charset">Localization</link></title>
________________________________________________________-->
     <title><link linkend="charset">本地化</link></title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=2e9a9782eabaaa726ff7af14e8ac1973 -->

     <itemizedlist>

<!--
Author: Jeff Davis <jdavis@postgresql.org>
2023-03-10 [c45dc7ffb] initdb: derive encoding from locale for ICU; similar to
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=684435d750a0f40b877c7c43aed80690 sig_cn_org=c2cf72b5575c5ea9edac9ccfe167433d source=16.8 
       <para>
        Determine the default encoding from the locale when using
        <acronym>ICU</acronym> (Jeff Davis)
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;c45dc7ffb">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        从区域设置中确定默认编码，当使用
        <acronym>ICU</acronym>时 (Jeff Davis)
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;c45dc7ffb">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=684435d750a0f40b877c7c43aed80690 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=ba74c332d1309129349dd49149feb7fa sig_cn_org=67fed737457eed499c962bb23ca40fa1 source=16.8 
       <para>
        Previously the default was always <literal>UTF-8</literal>.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        之前的默认值始终是<literal>UTF-8</literal>。
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=ba74c332d1309129349dd49149feb7fa -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Jeff Davis <jdavis@postgresql.org>
      Date:   Fri Jun 16 10:27:32 2023 -0700
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=77de324804c872673295e98f0b30acd8 sig_cn_org=7214b6ffb33f3c12f501de3c5c87a08b source=16.8 
       <para>
        Have <link linkend="sql-createdatabase"><command>CREATE
        DATABASE</command></link> and <link
        linkend="sql-createcollation"><command>CREATE
        COLLATION</command></link>'s <literal>LOCALE</literal> options, and
        <link linkend="app-initdb"><application>initdb</application></link>
        and <link
        linkend="app-createdb"><application>createdb</application></link>
        <option>-&minus;locale</option> options, control
        non-<application>libc</application> collation providers (Jeff
        Davis)
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        使用 <link linkend="sql-createdatabase"><command>CREATE
        DATABASE</command></link> 和 <link
        linkend="sql-createcollation"><command>CREATE
        COLLATION</command></link> 的 <literal>LOCALE</literal> 选项，以及
        <link linkend="app-initdb"><application>initdb</application></link>
        和 <link
        linkend="app-createdb"><application>createdb</application></link>
        <option>--locale</option> 选项，控制非
        <application>libc</application> 的排序规则提供程序 (Jeff
        Davis)
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=77de324804c872673295e98f0b30acd8 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=fc5963ee7e1140529e34059ad1929c92 sig_cn_org=49f5b40e46bdc7bddc51273e584be7f9 source=16.8 
       <para>
        Previously they only controlled <application>libc</application>
        providers.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        之前他们只控制了<application>libc</application>提供者。
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=fc5963ee7e1140529e34059ad1929c92 -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Peter Eisentraut <peter@eisentraut.org>
2023-03-10 [0d21d4b9b] Add standard collation UNICODE
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=95b4ba978e24557d4671366f11bd13e4 sig_cn_org=1c702fedb487f695be30b559598879a7 source=16.8 
       <para>
        Add predefined collations <literal>unicode</literal> and
        <literal>ucs_basic</literal> (Peter Eisentraut)
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;0d21d4b9b">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        添加预定义的排序规则<literal>unicode</literal>和
        <literal>ucs_basic</literal>（Peter Eisentraut）
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;0d21d4b9b">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=95b4ba978e24557d4671366f11bd13e4 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=c75f5feeaa77400278bce3967147f6c8 sig_cn_org=e9e620f8ad17b3ab796c51af2f6c44de source=16.8 
       <para>
        This only works if <acronym>ICU</acronym> support is enabled.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        这仅在启用了<acronym>ICU</acronym>支持时才有效。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=c75f5feeaa77400278bce3967147f6c8 -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Peter Eisentraut <peter@eisentraut.org>
2023-03-08 [30a53b792] Allow tailoring of ICU locales with custom rules
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=95380e7ef22301a540b959b9b509f042 sig_cn_org=85531957ebca89e099a887f90c885d1c source=16.8 
       <para>
        Allow custom <acronym>ICU</acronym> collation rules to be created
        (Peter Eisentraut)
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;30a53b792">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        允许创建自定义<acronym>ICU</acronym>排序规则
        （Peter Eisentraut）
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;30a53b792">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=95380e7ef22301a540b959b9b509f042 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=db3690fd0a9344fb2dc360fa96e84d52 sig_cn_org=4e45b2e7d2ebde8bba34d742749fa9dd source=16.8 
       <para>
        This is done using <link
        linkend="sql-createcollation"><command>CREATE
        COLLATION</command></link>'s new <literal>RULES</literal>
        clause, as well as new options for <link
        linkend="sql-createdatabase"><command>CREATE
        DATABASE</command></link>, <link
        linkend="app-createdb"><application>createdb</application></link>,
        and <link
        linkend="app-initdb"><application>initdb</application></link>.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        这是通过使用<link
        linkend="sql-createcollation"><command>CREATE
        COLLATION</command></link>的新<literal>RULES</literal>
        子句完成的，以及为<link
        linkend="sql-createdatabase"><command>CREATE
        DATABASE</command></link>、<link
        linkend="app-createdb"><application>createdb</application></link>
        和<link
        linkend="app-initdb"><application>initdb</application></link>
        提供的新选项。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=db3690fd0a9344fb2dc360fa96e84d52 -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Peter Eisentraut <peter@eisentraut.org>
2023-01-03 [bf03cfd16] Windows support in pg_import_system_collations
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=ef61e9aeebed36708cfd746338604dcb sig_cn_org=ded11b80e0a1f4fe9c1e450d1672b8f8 source=16.8 
       <para>
        Allow <systemitem class="osname">Windows</systemitem> to import
        system locales automatically (Juan José Santamaría Flecha)
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;bf03cfd16">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        允许<systemitem class="osname">Windows</systemitem>自动导入系统区域设置
        （Juan José Santamaría Flecha）
        <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;bf03cfd16">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=ef61e9aeebed36708cfd746338604dcb -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=b7d3e4fa2bff399c946dba6323a53085 sig_cn_org=d8d3d2a5a9950c8a1da2bb779a6cd2e8 source=16.8 
       <para>
        Previously, only <acronym>ICU</acronym> locales could be imported
        on <systemitem class="osname">Windows</systemitem>.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        以前，只有<acronym>ICU</acronym>语言环境可以在
        <systemitem class="osname">Windows</systemitem>上导入。
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=b7d3e4fa2bff399c946dba6323a53085 -->
      </listitem>

     </itemizedlist>

    </sect4>

   </sect3>

   <sect3 id="release-16-logical">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=eb0cc6f28d5a62da9c8aa33738ebd72d sig_cn_org=ebab24a834caa554d1abdf0e8bd252f9 source=15.7 
    <title><link linkend="logical-replication">Logical Replication</link></title>
________________________________________________________-->
    <title><link linkend="logical-replication">逻辑复制</link></title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=eb0cc6f28d5a62da9c8aa33738ebd72d -->

    <itemizedlist>

<!--
Author: Andres Freund <andres@anarazel.de>
2023-04-08 [0fdab27ad] Allow logical decoding on standbys
Author: Andres Freund <andres@anarazel.de>
2023-04-07 [be87200ef] Support invalidating replication slots due to horizon an
Author: Andres Freund <andres@anarazel.de>
2023-04-08 [26669757b] Handle logical slot conflicts on standby
-->

     <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=84d3eac8c96e0aad2249aba7e6d61d8d sig_cn_org=ffe068ea7cd2de6ca4daf5ebb6c3a556 source=16.8 
      <para>
       Allow <link linkend="logicaldecoding">logical decoding</link>
       on standbys (Bertrand Drouvot, Andres Freund, Amit Khandekar)
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;0fdab27ad">&sect;</ulink>
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;be87200ef">&sect;</ulink>
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;26669757b">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
       允许备用服务器上的<link linkend="logicaldecoding">逻辑解码</link>
       （Bertrand Drouvot、Andres Freund、Amit Khandekar）
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;0fdab27ad">&sect;</ulink>
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;be87200ef">&sect;</ulink>
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;26669757b">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=84d3eac8c96e0aad2249aba7e6d61d8d -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=a21e27abaa68e076849464c7f82954da sig_cn_org=012cd8c63e885879734ecb10e2aec3f0 source=16.8 
      <para>
       Snapshot <acronym>WAL</acronym> records are
       required for logical slot creation but cannot be
       created on standbys.  To avoid delays, the new function <link
       linkend="functions-snapshot-synchronization-table"><function>pg_log_standby_snapshot()</function></link>
       allows creation of such records.
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
       快照<acronym>WAL</acronym>记录是逻辑槽创建所必需的，但无法在备用
       节点上创建。为了避免延迟，新的函数<link
       linkend="functions-snapshot-synchronization-table"><function>pg_log_standby_snapshot()</function></link>
       允许创建此类记录。
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=a21e27abaa68e076849464c7f82954da -->
     </listitem>

<!--
Author: Amit Kapila <akapila@postgresql.org>
2022-12-26 [5de94a041] Add 'logical_decoding_mode' GUC.
Author: Amit Kapila <akapila@postgresql.org>
2023-01-30 [1e8b61735] Rename GUC logical_decoding_mode to logical_replication_
Author: Amit Kapila <akapila@postgresql.org>
2023-02-02 [9f2213a7c] Allow the logical_replication_mode to be used on the sub
-->

     <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=48bef1fb05aa234636585676dfb6db34 sig_cn_org=0a496ac355be23177aaf9f26ea682300 source=16.8 
      <para>
       Add server variable to control how logical decoding publishers
       transfer changes and how subscribers apply them (Shi Yu)
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;5de94a041">&sect;</ulink>
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;1e8b61735">&sect;</ulink>
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;9f2213a7c">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
       添加服务器变量以控制逻辑解码发布者如何传输更改以及订阅者如何应用它们
       (Shi Yu)
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;5de94a041">&sect;</ulink>
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;1e8b61735">&sect;</ulink>
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;9f2213a7c">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=48bef1fb05aa234636585676dfb6db34 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=4238b8c9719088cc8466032a2e5ad39b sig_cn_org=0af87a6c15aecf2ddf2789b87fe1ee49 source=16.8 
      <para>
       The variable is <link
       linkend="guc-debug-logical-replication-streaming"><varname>debug_logical_replication_streaming</varname></link>.
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
       该变量是<link
       linkend="guc-debug-logical-replication-streaming"><varname>debug_logical_replication_streaming</varname></link>。
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=4238b8c9719088cc8466032a2e5ad39b -->
     </listitem>

<!--
Author: Amit Kapila <akapila@postgresql.org>
2023-03-23 [ecb696527] Allow logical replication to copy tables in binary forma
-->

     <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=e2256ead79fad337ce6d09e0023b6578 sig_cn_org=98e2dab963d2b96362c4a27062dcba9f source=16.8 
      <para>
       Allow logical replication initial table synchronization to copy
       rows in binary format (Melih Mutlu)
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;ecb696527">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
       允许逻辑复制初始表同步以二进制格式复制行 (Melih Mutlu)
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;ecb696527">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=e2256ead79fad337ce6d09e0023b6578 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=8e1826a253624b2763c5b1a296c47fcf sig_cn_org=eede1d857fc594b19d85a471581caa48 source=16.8 
      <para>
       This is only possible for subscriptions marked as binary.
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
       这仅适用于标记为二进制的订阅。
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=8e1826a253624b2763c5b1a296c47fcf -->
     </listitem>

<!--
Author: Amit Kapila <akapila@postgresql.org>
2023-01-09 [216a78482] Perform apply of large transactions by parallel workers.
Author: Amit Kapila <akapila@postgresql.org>
2023-01-10 [cd06ccd78] Document the newly added wait events added by commit 216
Author: Amit Kapila <akapila@postgresql.org>
2023-02-16 [fce003cfd] Add a new wait state and use it when sending data in the
-->

     <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=8aaf3a01eafc7f85a6f276024dd4f2a2 sig_cn_org=3ed85f8539fe67f31b2573ab493344a7 source=16.8 
      <para>
       Allow parallel application of logical replication (Hou Zhijie,
       Wang Wei, Amit Kapila)
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;216a78482">&sect;</ulink>
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;cd06ccd78">&sect;</ulink>
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;fce003cfd">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
       允许逻辑复制的并行应用（侯志杰，王伟，Amit Kapila）
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;216a78482">&sect;</ulink>
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;cd06ccd78">&sect;</ulink>
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;fce003cfd">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=8aaf3a01eafc7f85a6f276024dd4f2a2 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=9d3cc821b097a11abe88592b1b158c3b sig_cn_org=2c5ae7cf733adf037ff2e9d75da12c69 source=16.8 
      <para>
       The <link linkend="sql-createsubscription"><command>CREATE
       SUBSCRIPTION</command></link> <option>STREAMING</option>
       option now supports <literal>parallel</literal> to enable
       application of large transactions by parallel workers.  The number
       of parallel workers is controlled by the new server variable <link
       linkend="guc-max-parallel-apply-workers-per-subscription"><varname>max_parallel_apply_workers_per_subscription</varname></link>.
       Wait events <link
       linkend="wait-event-activity-table"><literal>LogicalParallelApplyMain</literal></link>,
       <literal>LogicalParallelApplyStateChange</literal>, and
       <literal>LogicalApplySendData</literal> were also added.  Column
       <structfield>leader_pid</structfield> was added to system view <link
       linkend="monitoring-pg-stat-subscription"><structname>pg_stat_subscription</structname></link>
       to track parallel activity.
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
       <link linkend="sql-createsubscription"><command>CREATE
       SUBSCRIPTION</command></link> <option>STREAMING</option>
       选项现在支持<literal>parallel</literal>，以通过并行工作者应用大事务。
       并行工作者的数量由新的服务器变量<link
       linkend="guc-max-parallel-apply-workers-per-subscription"><varname>max_parallel_apply_workers_per_subscription</varname></link>
       控制。新增了等待事件<link
       linkend="wait-event-activity-table"><literal>LogicalParallelApplyMain</literal></link>、
       <literal>LogicalParallelApplyStateChange</literal>和
       <literal>LogicalApplySendData</literal>。系统视图<link
       linkend="monitoring-pg-stat-subscription"><structname>pg_stat_subscription</structname></link>
       新增了列<structfield>leader_pid</structfield>，用于跟踪并行活动。
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=9d3cc821b097a11abe88592b1b158c3b -->
     </listitem>

<!--
Author: Amit Kapila <akapila@postgresql.org>
2023-03-15 [89e46da5e] Allow the use of indexes other than PK and REPLICA IDENT
-->

     <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=6ad6c00cb341a56007de309802d07a5b sig_cn_org=d0e05ffa2d3351ec9aad4e0bc926db00 source=16.8 
      <para>
       Improve performance for <link
       linkend="logical-replication-architecture">logical replication
       apply</link> without a primary key (Onder Kalaci, Amit Kapila)
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;89e46da5e">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
       提高逻辑复制应用在没有主键情况下的性能
       (<link linkend="logical-replication-architecture">逻辑复制架构</link>)
       (Onder Kalaci, Amit Kapila)
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;89e46da5e">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=6ad6c00cb341a56007de309802d07a5b -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=81cfc0fc12426d18f0bf7e65033925c7 sig_cn_org=5a95b8c6d7f454de17a313e36e4571cb source=16.8 
      <para>
       Specifically, <literal>REPLICA IDENTITY FULL</literal> can now
       use btree indexes rather than sequentially scanning the table to
       find matches.
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
       具体来说，<literal>REPLICA IDENTITY FULL</literal>现在可以使用btree索引，
       而不是顺序扫描表来找到匹配项。
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=81cfc0fc12426d18f0bf7e65033925c7 -->
     </listitem>

<!--
Author: Amit Kapila <akapila@postgresql.org>
2022-07-21 [366283961] Allow users to skip logical replication of data having o
Author: Amit Kapila <akapila@postgresql.org>
2022-09-08 [875693019] Raise a warning if there is a possibility of data from m
-->

     <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=10eb5909fa9b839e57d927255891ad6c sig_cn_org=45f4438aaf71b3418eb89abc23a9789f source=16.8 
      <para>
       Allow logical replication subscribers to process only changes that
       have no origin (Vignesh C, Amit Kapila)
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;366283961">&sect;</ulink>
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;875693019">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
       允许逻辑复制订阅者仅处理没有来源的更改
       （Vignesh C, Amit Kapila）
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;366283961">&sect;</ulink>
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;875693019">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=10eb5909fa9b839e57d927255891ad6c -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=23d5c28df54b2d7830730d0aa7eb880f sig_cn_org=da4910569aeff354df931be3278c5998 source=16.8 
      <para>
       This can be used to avoid replication loops.  This is controlled
       by the new <literal>CREATE SUBSCRIPTION ... ORIGIN</literal> option.
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
       这可以用来避免复制循环。这由新的<literal>CREATE SUBSCRIPTION ... ORIGIN</literal>
       选项控制。
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=23d5c28df54b2d7830730d0aa7eb880f -->
     </listitem>

<!--
Author: Robert Haas <rhaas@postgresql.org>
2023-04-04 [1e10d49b6] Perform logical replication actions as the table owner.
Author: Robert Haas <rhaas@postgresql.org>
2023-04-04 [482675987] Add a run_as_owner option to subscriptions.
-->

     <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=6708c15dd1b4159f7a035f5b054861f4 sig_cn_org=6de8d688bd0c47bcbd32aa2b29d76522 source=16.8 
      <para>
       Perform logical replication <link
       linkend="sql-select"><command>SELECT</command></link> and
       <acronym>DML</acronym> actions as the table owner (Robert Haas)
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;1e10d49b6">&sect;</ulink>
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;482675987">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
       以表所有者的身份执行逻辑复制<link
       linkend="sql-select"><command>SELECT</command></link>和
       <acronym>DML</acronym>操作（Robert Haas）
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;1e10d49b6">&sect;</ulink>
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;482675987">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=6708c15dd1b4159f7a035f5b054861f4 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=e436cc5a11a07f053b0d19b546963529 sig_cn_org=12713d141048a1c7c590a3cabfb1479a source=16.8 
      <para>
       This improves security and now requires subscription
       owners to be either superusers or to have <link
       linkend="sql-set-role"><command>SET ROLE</command></link>
       permission on all roles owning tables in the replication set.
       The previous behavior of performing all operations as the
       subscription owner can be enabled with the subscription <link
       linkend="sql-createsubscription"><option>run_as_owner</option></link>
       option.
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
       这提高了安全性，现在要求订阅所有者必须是超级用户，或者对复制集
       中所有拥有表的角色具有<link linkend="sql-set-role"><command>SET ROLE</command></link>
       权限。之前以订阅所有者身份执行所有操作的行为可以通过订阅
       <link linkend="sql-createsubscription"><option>run_as_owner</option></link>
       选项启用。
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=e436cc5a11a07f053b0d19b546963529 -->
     </listitem>

<!--
Author: Tom Lane <tgl@sss.pgh.pa.us>
2023-01-22 [5a3a95385] Track logrep apply workers' last start times to avoid us
-->

     <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=78fbd6a077a76a9c16aca1f523fba464 sig_cn_org=6e3cd2a0fc8ae31899384cf72f5cedb4 source=16.8 
      <para>
       Have <link
       linkend="guc-wal-retrieve-retry-interval"><varname>wal_retrieve_retry_interval</varname></link>
       operate on a per-subscription basis (Nathan Bossart)
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;5a3a95385">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
       让<link
       linkend="guc-wal-retrieve-retry-interval"><varname>wal_retrieve_retry_interval</varname></link>
       按每个订阅的基础进行操作（Nathan Bossart）
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;5a3a95385">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=78fbd6a077a76a9c16aca1f523fba464 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=06502e775a17387e48904c70491a9508 sig_cn_org=977a2f0163bf3e5a211c30461e4fe205 source=16.8 
      <para>
       Previously the retry time was applied
       globally.  This also adds wait events <link
       linkend="wait-event-lwlock-table">><literal>LogicalRepLauncherDSA</literal></link>
       and <literal>LogicalRepLauncherHash</literal>.
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
       之前，重试时间是全局应用的。此更改还添加了等待事件<link
       linkend="wait-event-lwlock-table">><literal>LogicalRepLauncherDSA</literal></link>
       和<literal>LogicalRepLauncherHash</literal>。
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=06502e775a17387e48904c70491a9508 -->
     </listitem>

    </itemizedlist>

   </sect3>

   <sect3 id="release-16-utility">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=0e46664130e2edfe41fbfc4db308e7d9 sig_cn_org=2bb3a00fc3cc909909d82423d80d1d62 source=15.7 
