       Allow subqueries in the <literal>FROM</literal> clause to omit
       aliases (Dean Rasheed)
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;bcedd8f5f">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
       允许在<literal>FROM</literal>子句中省略别名（Dean Rasheed）
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;bcedd8f5f">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=a4aee45748495706c5abbcd1361b8101 -->
     </listitem>

<!--
Author: Peter Eisentraut <peter@eisentraut.org>
2023-03-05 [102a5c164] SQL JSON path enhanced numeric literals
-->

     <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=0291e47e310dd6a37086bc614809c909 sig_cn_org=c5c9fba8ec98ea17c878751085f02ab3 source=16.8 
      <para>
       Add support for enhanced numeric literals in
       <acronym>SQL/JSON</acronym> paths (Peter Eisentraut)
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;102a5c164">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
       在<acronym>SQL/JSON</acronym>路径中添加对增强型数字字面量的支持
       （Peter Eisentraut）
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;102a5c164">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=0291e47e310dd6a37086bc614809c909 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=0ae6252241443da6fffc42f6552078e2 sig_cn_org=1c1c36af3b4b8f02e664c34e3027ce41 source=16.8 
      <para>
       For example, allow hexadecimal, octal, and binary integers and
       underscores between digits.
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
       例如，允许十六进制、八进制和二进制整数，以及数字之间的下划线。
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=0ae6252241443da6fffc42f6552078e2 -->
     </listitem>

    </itemizedlist>

