        Add <application>LZ4</application> and
        <application>Zstandard</application> compression to
        <application>pg_dump</application> (Georgios Kokolatos, Justin
        Pryzby)
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        添加<application>LZ4</application>和
        <application>Zstandard</application>压缩到
        <application>pg_dump</application>（Georgios Kokolatos，Justin
        Pryzby）
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=231cf210351d281f234cfe1fa614194e -->
      </listitem>

