       linkend="app-pgverifybackup"><application>pg_verifybackup</application></link>
       (Masahiko Sawada)
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;d07c2948b">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
       为<link
       linkend="app-pgverifybackup"><application>pg_verifybackup</application></link>
       添加进度报告支持（Masahiko Sawada）
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;d07c2948b">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=516a858942090048204883970256a481 -->
     </listitem>

<!--
Author: Heikki Linnakangas <heikki.linnakangas@iki.fi>
2023-02-23 [009eeee74] pg_rewind: Fix determining TLI when server was just prom
Author: Heikki Linnakangas <heikki.linnakangas@iki.fi>
2023-02-27 [0a0500207] pg_rewind: Remove notice in docs about running CHECKPOIN
-->

     <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=5d19322a2cb49bbeb1ff849961a7afee sig_cn_org=fa8229f34c221bc8b81ec6a83ce2bd37 source=16.8 
      <para>
       Allow <link
       linkend="app-pgrewind"><application>pg_rewind</application></link>
       to properly track timeline changes (Heikki Linnakangas)
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;009eeee74">&sect;</ulink>
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;0a0500207">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
       允许<link
       linkend="app-pgrewind"><application>pg_rewind</application></link>
       正确跟踪时间线的变化（Heikki Linnakangas）
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;009eeee74">&sect;</ulink>
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;0a0500207">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=5d19322a2cb49bbeb1ff849961a7afee -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=89a6e0f8480c051f621ff3ee09874136 sig_cn_org=ee9b04a0a0a8e54e3ed7115b6ed3367e source=16.8 
      <para>
       Previously if <application>pg_rewind</application> was run after
       a timeline switch but before a checkpoint was issued, it might
       incorrectly determine that a rewind was unnecessary.
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
       之前，如果在时间线切换后但在检查点发出之前运行
       <application>pg_rewind</application>，它可能会错误地判断不需要回滚。
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=89a6e0f8480c051f621ff3ee09874136 -->
     </listitem>

<!--
Author: Daniel Gustafsson <dgustafsson@postgresql.org>
2022-09-14 [8b60db774] Handle SIGTERM in pg_receivewal and pg_recvlogical
-->

     <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=fa314473a9d7b93cfc78f4d82540e243 sig_cn_org=b2eeaab38c2a91c4a915d52979964d68 source=16.8 
      <para>
       Have <link
       linkend="app-pgreceivewal"><application>pg_receivewal</application></link>
       and <link
       linkend="app-pgrecvlogical"><application>pg_recvlogical</application></link>
       cleanly exit on <literal>SIGTERM</literal> (Christoph Berg)
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;8b60db774">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
       让<link
       linkend="app-pgreceivewal"><application>pg_receivewal</application></link>
       和<link
       linkend="app-pgrecvlogical"><application>pg_recvlogical</application></link>
       在接收到<literal>SIGTERM</literal>信号时干净地退出 (Christoph Berg)
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;8b60db774">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=fa314473a9d7b93cfc78f4d82540e243 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=225dec6e65091411f196cae6d126957e sig_cn_org=fff213914e762d487140bba96812645d source=16.8 
      <para>
       This signal is often used by <application>systemd</application>.
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
       此信号通常由<application>systemd</application>使用。
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=225dec6e65091411f196cae6d126957e -->
     </listitem>

    </itemizedlist>

